data.description: Beautiful, well maintained home in highly desired Acadia Place. Just two blocks from Owens Elementary school, this immaculately landscaped home in South Tyler features a split floor plan with an oversized master bedroom, his and hers closets, soaking tub and stand up shower and shower/tub combo in the gorgeous guest bathroom. Easy to maintain ceramic tile flooring in common areas with carpet in all four bedrooms. Brand new microwave. High end dishwasher and garbage disposal are 18 months old. Freshly painted interior, gas outlet on patio for your grill, 2 car garage, security system conveys (not under contract), and no HOA fees.  Located just south of Loop 49, you'll have easy access to FRESH and dinning/shopping at The Village at Cumberland Park. Schedule your showing today!
